{"tid":664354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"噁男馬路朝少女露鳥　還喚：妹妹來幫我的忙","createTime":"2018-05-14T04:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:32:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad69a0ab291a69e021fe85a72f061012391d03a6","tid":664354,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"桃園一名林姓男子（31歲），前年7 月1 日下午4 時12分許，騎車行經桃園市八德區一處道路時，見當時14歲的少女獨自走在人行道上，竟拉下長褲拉鏈公然露鳥，還抓著生殖器向被害人稱：「妹妹，你可以過來幫我的忙嗎？」被害少女嚇得花容失色，趕忙逃離現場報警處理，警獲報立即調閱監視器將露鳥男逮捕到案送辦。<br />\n <br />\n林男到案時否認犯行，辯稱曾把機車借給他人，案發當天正在上班；但林男說不出借車的友人真實身分，向其工作的餐廳調閱出勤記錄，打卡時間卻是下午5時50分，加上被害人指証歷歷等情，桃園地院日前依公然猥褻罪判處拘役55日，可以1000元折算1日易科罰金。（突發中心張沛森／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353425/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353425%2F&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=315fd579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353425%2F&h=aa2a1c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353425/</a>"},{"pid":"deb034602facaf282e185141d0c1f6aa6ac3a1e9","tid":664354,"uid":141837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"所以話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35784b39a58c78578dcb46a50e603aa4a1b1a389","tid":664354,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"驚what"},{"pid":"16b190793f9c3f2ce61e050cb29bd2edd4a0f37e","tid":664354,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb034602facaf282e185141d0c1f6aa6ac3a1e9","tid":664354,"uid":141837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"所以話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img sr